title: America - The Best Of Musikladen Live (Studio 1975)
description:
America - The Best Of Musikladen Live 1975

MusikLaden, also known as Beat Club, was German television&#039;s leading rock music series in the 1960s and &#039;70s, featuring many top acts from both Europe and the U.S. This video features a full 45-minute performance by the folk-rock group America taped for MusikLaden in 1975, featuring many of their biggest hits. Selections include "Horse With No Name," "Ventura Highway," "I Need You," "Lonely People," and "Don&#039;t Cross the River."
